locality: Between Ambovombe and Tsiombe, on Route National 10, 12 km E of Tsiombe; along low calcareous outcrop S of road.

Sud, 25 km east of Amboasary, 50 km west of Fort-Dauphin (Taolanaro), near Res. nat. Andohahela, Parcelle 3. Dry spiny shrubland with Decarya madagascariensis, Alluaudia comosa, A. dumosa, Euphorbia stenoclada and other terete Euphorbia, on sandy lateritic soil.
District d'Ambovombe - Poste de Beloha - Canton de Tranomaro - Plateau de Karimbola (sous race Mahafaly).
Sud-Ouest : Plateau calcaire à l'Est du Lac Tsimanampetsotsa, sur la limite Nord de la R.N. X.
